The major parameters in these records: station and sea level pressure; dry bulb, wet bulb, and dewpoint temperature; humidity; winds; precipitation; snowfall and snow depth; clouds; and weather.  These highly detailed observations range from 2-4  times daily.  </dct:description>         <dcat:keyword>{observations</dcat:keyword>         <dcat:keyword>weather</dcat:keyword>
